Source: libfacts
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Warren MacEvoy <wmacevoy@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), g++
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/wmacevoy/facts

Package: libfacts-1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight C/C++ testing library
 Facts is a tiny, beginner-friendly C/C++ testing library. It provides
 FACTS(name) groups and FACT(a,op,b) checks with readable failure messages.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries: libfacts (C) and libfacts++ (C++).

Package: libfacts-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libfacts-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight C/C++ testing library (development files)
 Facts is a tiny, beginner-friendly C/C++ testing library. It provides
 FACTS(name) groups and FACT(a,op,b) checks with readable failure messages.
 .
 This package contains the header files, static libraries, and pkg-config
 files for development.
